name: Hamilton U.S. Bond YIELD MAXIMIZER TM ETF
longDescription: HBND will seek to achieve its investment objective by investing primarily in a portfolio of bond exchange traded funds, with an emphasis on selecting those holding US treasuries. HBND may also hold cash and cash equivalents or other money market instruments in order to meet its obligations. The investment objective of HBND is to deliver attractive monthly income, while providing exposure primarily to U.S. treasuries through a portfolio of bond exchange traded funds. To supplement distribution income earned on the exchange traded fund holdings, mitigate risk and reduce volatility, HBND will employ a covered call option writing program.
